Starting an Instagram presence from zero is slow. Our premium aged Instagram accounts, including options with real organic followers, let you begin from an established presence instead of an empty profile.

### What you gain

1. **Accelerated growth**, skip the cold-start grind.
2. **Instant social proof**, an audience that is already there.
3. **More effective campaigns**, content and ads land with built-in credibility.
4. **A verification-ready base**, established accounts are stronger candidates for the blue tick.

Each account is hand-selected for quality and longevity, so you start strong rather than from scratch.

{% callout variant="tip" title="Go further with verification" %}
Pair an aged Instagram account with our [Verification Badge](/docs/asset-overview/verification-badge) service to add the blue tick and unlock maximum authority. [Ask our team](/docs/questions-bank/support) for current options and pricing.
{% /callout %}
